    Scope and Contents
Records of the Committee includes minutes, correspondence, grant applications, proposals, and requests and other materials having to do with the Committee's allocation of money from the $150,000 Ford Foundation Venture Fund at SSU.
Projects funded include the Learning Center, the Oceanography projects, Sangamon Poets, the Springfield Area Neighborhood Organization and the Minority Service Center.  Mark Erenburg (Springfield Urban League).  James Margin (Illinois Office of Collective Bargaining).  Peter Katela (Illinois State Senate), Dick Johnston and Mark Heyman received Faculty Experience grants.  
  
